Monday, June 22, 1998

MOTION DOCKET

97-2003. State v. Lindsey.

Brown C.P. Nos. 97-2015 and 97-2064. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Court of Common Pleas of Brown County. Upon consideration of the motion of Lori Ann McGinnis, Assistant State Public Defender, to review exhibits transmitted under seal,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the motion to review exhibits transmitted under seal be, and hereby is, granted.
